data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single family home in Cherokee County Georgia sits on 1.70 acres of land. This corner lot home contains an ample amount of living space upstairs and 2 newly finished rooms in the basement that can be used for an office and entertaining. It has a 2 car garage and a large deck to sit out and enjoy nature at its best! Must see this home, upgrades are here and the basement adds even more living space to enjoy.
